		<article class="col-sm-8 col-lg-9">
			<div class="intro col-xs-12" style="background-color:#545962">
				<h4>Collections and research</h4>
				
			</div>
			<div class="main col-sm-12">
				<div class="headerImg">
											<img src="http://www.mccord-museum.qc.ca/app/uploads/2015/07/centre_archives_documentation_header.jpg" alt="">
															</div>
				<div class="text col-xs-12 col-md-8">
				
					<div class="title">
						<h1>Archives and Documentation Centre</h1>
					</div>

					<div class="tiny">
						<p>Researchers from all fields of study can access part of the McCord Museum&#8217;s collections by consulting our online database or <em>The Museum System</em>, an even more complete computerized catalogue of our collection available on-site at the Archives and Documentation Centre.</p>
<p>Over 750 fonds and collections of textual archives, as well as a major collection of photographs, are available for public consultation. The Archives and Documentation Centre also offers users access to a reference library of 9000 works and specialized periodicals, in addition to the more than 2500 titles in its rare book collection.</p>
<h4>Rules and legislation</h4>
<p>All visitors to the Archives and Documentation Centre must follow the <strong>Rules for Users of the McCord Museum Reading Room</strong>.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/app/uploads/2015/06/cad_reglement_consultation_2015_en.pdf" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'download', 'http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/app/uploads/2015/06/cad_reglement_consultation_2015_en.pdf');" class="download">Rules</a></p>
<h4>Photographic services and copyright</h4>
<p>To use images from the McCord Museum&#8217;s collections, please consult the <strong><a href="http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/en/photographic-services-and-copyright/" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/en/photographic-services-and-copyright/', 'Photographic Services and Copyright');">Photographic Services and Copyright</a></strong> page.</p>
<h4>Schedule</h4>
<p><strong>Please note that The Archives and Documentation Centre will be closed from December 18, 2015 to January 4, 2016 inclusive.</strong><br />
The Archives and Documentation Centre is open to the public, by appointment only, Tuesday to Thursday, from 9:30 a.m. to 12:30 p.m. and from 1:30 p.m. to 5:00 p.m.<br />
The Archives and Documentation Centre is closed on legal holidays.</p>
					</div>

																		<div class="title">
								<h2>To make an appointment</h2>
							</div>

							<div class="tiny">
								<p>Email the completed form below to submit a research request to the Centre.<br />
<strong><a href="mailto:reference.mccord@mccord-stewart.ca">reference.mccord@mccord-stewart.ca</a></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/app/uploads/2015/06/cad_formulaire_demande_de_recherche_2015_fr_en.docx" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/app/uploads/2015/06/cad_formulaire_demande_de_recherche_2015_fr_en.docx', 'Research Request Form');" class="download">Research Request Form</a></p>
